name: Super Seedway
description:
Entry for Kenney Jam 2019! Are you ready to become the best car-dener around?

(Never before has a gardening game featured such a tired protagonist... You'll be able to garden so fast it'll drive you mad.)

Controls:

Movement - Arrow Keys (or WASD)

Jump - Spacebar

Interact - Up or W

Goal:

Unfortunately we weren't able to implement an end-game (the vault was going to open and you were going to have to fight and end the machine that makes all machines... or something), so you're free to garden to your heart's content (until your garden is full).
